Creative Phase

Creative Phase

01

Brief &Data Analysis

What’s the project about &what data will we use in input? What will trigger the creation of videos? Where will the videos be published in output?
Brief &Data Analysis

What’s the project about &what data will we use in input? What will trigger the creation of videos? Where will the videos be published in output?

02

Data Storyboard &Dashboard Mockup

We streamline every scene of the video with sketches, highlighting the variable data in each scene. Then, we design a mockup of the interface you’ll use to launch videos.
Data Storyboard &Dashboard Mockup

We streamline every scene of the video with sketches, highlighting the variable data in each scene. Then, we design a mockup of the interface you’ll use to launch videos.

03

Design

We define the style of the video through moodboards &style-frames. Then, we design the video, taking data-visualization &data variability into consideration
Design

We define the style of the video through moodboards &style-frames. Then, we design the video, taking data-visualization &data variability into consideration

04

Animation &Video Pilot

We complete the creative phase by adding animation, music and sound. We then create - still completely manually - two or three versions of the video customised with real life data. We call these Video Pilots.

Animation &

Video Pilot


We complete the creative phase by adding animation, music and sound. We then create -still completely manually- two or three versions of the video customised with real life data. We call this Video Pilots.

Technical Phase

Technical Phase

05

Dashboard Dev &Data Integration

We kick-off the technical phase by creating &giving you access to the dashboard &integrating all the data in input as well as developing the video delivery in output.

Dashboard Dev &Data Integration


We kick-off the technical phase by creating &giving you access to the dashboard &integrating all the data in input as well as developing the video delivery in output.

06

Video Automation

It’s time to code the video pilot and transform it into a Template that speaks with the data and can be easily customised by our Algo platform.
Video Automation

It’s time to code the video pilot and transform it into a Template that speaks with the data and can be easily customised by our Algo platform.

07

Cloud Setup &Testing

We setup the dashboard &template in our cloud infrastructure and start rendering videos. Both our team and the client test the solution to find &solve bugs.
Cloud Setup &Testing

We setup the dashboard &template in our cloud infrastructure and start rendering videos. Both our team and the client test the solution to find &solve bugs.

08

Go Live

Your automated video campaign is live! Your team can now create videos everyday. During the whole live period, we’re reachable to make sure the campaign runs smoothly.

Go Live


Your automated video campaign is live! Your team can now create videos everyday. During the whole live period, we're reachable to make sure the campaign runs smoothly.
